Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo Oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear this is her first tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Five under on her first tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently she did it with\Nonly half a set of clubs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo is having quite the debut today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She did.\NBetter than we could have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Tsubura Adaniya? She should be\Nable to beat Tonbo's 67.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The new scores are up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura is in second!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Tsubura Adaniya\Nis sitting at two under.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The out course group just finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The in course group will finish last.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If a player using only a half set\Nwins this tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be big news.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura Adaniya is in second,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hinoki Otaha is in third.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all notable players.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a good place\Nto be on the last hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not going to be\Nhappy about that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can make the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't make the last two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he died, my husband said\Nhe wished to play in the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do it for his sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's making a big commotion about\Nthe new girl playing with a half set!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a lie, of course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe she's at five under.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Having two new irons in my bag\Nmade it much easier to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never gotten a score\Nlike this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The last group has just returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The top positions will\Nprobably stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The pairings tomorrow\Nwill be based on current standings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll probably be\Nplaying together tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to play with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The last group's scores are going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in 99th place with current score.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They added another name above mine.{\i0}\N{\i1}That puts me in one hundredth place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One hundredth place, again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in last place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She hit an eight on the first hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I have a chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixty-nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Another player with a score\Nin the sixties at the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A sixty-nine with a double par?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That puts her at seven under.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She played with a base of sixty-five?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Shima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a line drawn above\Nyour name like that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is like being told that \Nyou're good for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my husband said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Golf never goes the way you want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to prepare again\Nfor next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how much I love golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I got to play\Nwith you, Ms. Shima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to play with you again some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Toshima Village\NDisaster Management.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,About the Kyushu Women's Open\Nthat began today--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's a golf tournament, and--\N-Hurry up and say the important stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. A resident of this island and a\Nstudent at Tsuboi High school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're taking way too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Tonbo is in first place at her\Nfirst ever tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey! I wanted to say it!{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm the one who heard it first, after all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone! This calls for a celebration!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today was only the first day!{\i0}\N{\i1}The tournament is three days long!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That doesn't change the need to celebrate!{\i0}\N{\i1}Let's drink! Go Tonbo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't let me talk at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you took too long with your\Nbabbling nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least\Nturn the microphone off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Of course, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo is in first,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and Tsubura is in third.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving the island and\Ncompeting against so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how it feels for Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!\NTonbo's doing just fine, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's hard at work\Npracticing for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it will dry by tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the only clothes\Nshe has for the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't dry in time\NI'll lend her mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the poor girl alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ema Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ema?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ema Kurisu!\NI knew I'd heard of her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an incredibly talented title holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it already been ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a girl who's been winning\Nworld tournaments since she was twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A Japanese-American girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think her name was Ema Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A world junior champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, after that,\N her name stopped coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What has she been doing\Nfor the last decade?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A shark bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen a shark bite wound\Non the island before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hers looks the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's left-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I had heard about her championships,\Nbut never that she was a lefty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But the wedge she was just using\Nwas a right-handed club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Her 58 and putter are right handed,\Nbut everything else is left handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that stance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's putting her weight\Non her right foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called a one-axis swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, that's an interesting way\Nto apply her weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Will my daughter ever be\Nable to play golf again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Golf?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still not positive\Nshe'll ever walk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to start there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't hit it as far as I used to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My left leg...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to use lefty clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use these
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I can play again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are your 58 and putter right-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play the way I always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With small techniques, there shouldn't be\Ntoo much stress on my left ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I use bigger clubs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,my left ankle can't hold the weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"No weight shifting is\Nrequired during back swing."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do this I'll be able to swing\Nwithout putting weight on my left leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More. More.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to put more effort in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe then I can finally compete again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It took ten long years,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm finally competing again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My efforts paid off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You've played this course\Nhundreds of times!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've played this course\Nmore than anyone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitting under par should be no issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to get a stroke over 69.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting first place today. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My father will never be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Hinoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not Hinoki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Golf would be easy if you\Ncould improve by being scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't control your score.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand that, you don't\Nhave the right to be scolding others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like your attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She reminds me of how {\i0}\N{\i1}I used to enjoy playing golf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't have the attitude of{\i0}\N{\i1}someone about to compete in a tournament.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When we played golf\Non the island it was for fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make my dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to win and get into the Japan\NWomen's Amateur Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japan Women's Amateur?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win the Amateur Open,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and prove my true talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japan Junior and Japan Amateur Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With those two big titles,\NI'll be able to make it to the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I'll enter a pro tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win a pro tournament\Nwhile I'm still an amateur,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and join the pros myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of future do you want in golf?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the island because\NI wanted to learn more about golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't think I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You and all the other girls\Nhave goals and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all aiming\Nto be the best golfers you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that without having goals or\Ndreams like you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I shouldn't\Nbe playing golf at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe I wasn't serious enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday I got to play\Nwith a woman named Ms. Shima.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She made me realize I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The club!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to play golf\Njust because you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to push yourself to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just having the idea alone is\Nenough reason to put your all into golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo has evolved significantly since she\Ngot here, in both technique and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for talking to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hinoki Otoha. She's a grade above\Nme in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who she is. She was last year's\NKyushu Junior Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning I try to be myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can never quite do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My father scolds me to be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your motto, right? Doing your best \Nso that tomorrow you'll be your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you'll do better tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll be myself tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, thinking you'll do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means you'll never do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be saying that motto forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like people who say\N"if I had only tried my best."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that forever\Nand never actually try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They blame their inability on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you can be responsible for becoming\Nwho you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still early, but why\Ndon't we get ready to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to be my\Ntrue self starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the 9:46 group please\Nreport to the tee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, my name is Hata and \NI'll be your caddy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to playing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kyushu Junior Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japan Junior Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And the World Junior Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A high-skilled group\Nfitting for today's order!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And among the greats, there's Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Without any titles to her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no telling\Nhow far her ability goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see a{\i1} kobu {\i0}spinning a web.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be any wind today,\Njust like yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kobu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we call spiders back on the\Nisland.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They only spin webs on days\Nwhen the wind isn't too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Gon always says.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that some kind of bug, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No wind today, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tee is higher than usual.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her grip is higher than usual, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her stance is wider, too.{\i0}\N{\i1}Her distance from the ball, longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her backswing is bigger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She hit it as far as Tonbo did yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's added a bit more to everything.\NShe usually hits the ball far
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never seen Hinoki swing\Nlike that first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I got through to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My third shot will be from the left side\Nof the fairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hit my second shot from the\Nright side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I'll\Nhave to tee up from the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A tee shot like that will have\Nthe other players running scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remain quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have 420 yards to the third shot.{\i0}\N{\i1}I'll have to get there in two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no need to be scared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of weak swing is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what you call a good shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I haven't seen\Nyou do that in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga told me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! The{\i1} Great One Pattern{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the World Junior Champion,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A one-axis swing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} is characterized by aiming{\i0}\N{\i1}the sternum away from the ball.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bounce!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tee won't go in easily.{\i0}\N{\i1}Is it from all the sunshine recently?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She raised the tee.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going for a big shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hand-first stance with a driver? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:21:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Setting the ball in the middle?{\i0}\N{\i1}That will loft it like a vertical wall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to use the\Ntop half of the club face?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She dropped her stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Third one from the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Sunshine Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How does she make it roll like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The third line from the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The mowing lines of the fairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mowing lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,According to an old pro,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,on a long hole, you should\Naim for a bright spot on the fairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an old technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By a bright spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he meant areas of the fairway\Nthat appear brighter in color.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the mowing lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's lined up with Ema Kurisu's ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think a low shot like that\Nwould travel that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo took into account\Nthe ground being dry and hard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and hit a shot she knew would roll far.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How was she able to calculate that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually aiming for the fifth one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's a new day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.30,0:23:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give you advice\Nlike Mr. Igarashi does.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Hajime!\NYou have something that Igaiga doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:23:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I do? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack-in-the-box Golf
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo! What is it that I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face isn't scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
